    "subtitle": "Why was PATA & CÃO born?",
    "p1": "We know that loving a pet also brings challenges. The pet market is growing, but finding reliable services is still difficult. Have you ever felt lost jumping from app to app, unsure whether that boarding house or dog walker is really safe? Us too.",
